Module jdk.jdi
Package com.sun.jdi

Interface DoubleValue

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<DoubleValue>, Mirror, PrimitiveValue, Value
public interface DoubleValue
extends PrimitiveValue, Comparable<DoubleValue>
Provides access to a primitive double value in the target VM.
Since:
1.3
